title: 038 - Cherikee Red
description: On today's show, the guys discuss some of their favorite neighborhood games as kids, some old pop brands, including the legend of Cherikee Red, a Navy Fighter Pilot successfully locking on to alien aircraft, Nick's feud with Guy Fieri, they look into what they're excited to watch this weekend including the new Tom Hardy Capone movie, and much more. Have a safe weekend, and enjoy.
